race.comment: FEARLESS BEAR (7) settled well back early on debut and boxed on fairly to finish fourth (22.57) at this track over 390m. Should be much improved and can open winning account. PAW XELA (1) is a newcomer for the Robert Camilleri kennel with no trial form to work with. Gets her chance from the draw. Respect any moves in the market. PAW MONET (2) has her first outing without a trial but profiles nicely for this. Can sneak into the finish on debut. WESTERN'S PEACH (6) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.
